    "name": "Run Higher",
    "steam_appid": 3091150,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091150/extras/d54357bb3575287d5836489236a38051.avif?t=1765624246\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-----Run Higher-----</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run Higher offers you 16 exciting, unlockable levels where your goal is to climb to the top of each level as quickly as possible. Your best time is saved, allowing you to continually challenge yourself to improve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware! This isn’t just a simple running game – objects constantly fall from above and roll towards you. You need to skillfully dodge them, as getting hit too often means you'll have to restart. Your survival depends on your health bar, which shows how many hits you can still take.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fortunately, there are Three different power-ups to help you: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1. Health Refill</strong> - Restores your health bar so you can last longer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2. Power Shield</strong> - Provides you with a shield for a few seconds that deflects all falling objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3. Slow Motion Power-Up</strong> – Slows down everything for a short period of time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>17 MAPS</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091150/extras/34e2a02d42d51dc6b5a7247acb5151aa.poster.avif?t=1765624246\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091150/extras/34e2a02d42d51dc6b5a7247acb5151aa.webm?t=1765624246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091150/extras/34e2a02d42d51dc6b5a7247acb5151aa.mp4?t=1765624246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1. Run Mode</strong> - Classic running and dodging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2. Curve Run Mode</strong> - Running on curvy tracks that add extra challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3. Trap Mode</strong> - Levels with dangerous traps that test your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Run 8 Level</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Curve Run 8 Level</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Trap Run 1 Level</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you successfully complete a race, you earn XP (experience points) needed to unlock new levels. Alternatively, you can trade your XP for fun hats to wear during each race, customizing your character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently, there are 17 different levels and a total of 10 different hats – enough to keep challenging yourself and your friends. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for an exciting adventure full of obstacles and challenges in Run Higher!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hunt Your Time</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091150/extras/6567eb8fdca6f064e18491c3da4aa77a.poster.avif?t=1765624246\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091150/extras/6567eb8fdca6f064e18491c3da4aa77a.webm?t=1765624246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091150/extras/6567eb8fdca6f064e18491c3da4aa77a.mp4?t=1765624246\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
